    "attributes": {
        "action": "Cap Legal Aid to 2 hours",
        "additional_details": "We want legal aid to be capped to 2 hours, to reduce costs.\r\n \r\nWe believe Legal Aid has become a racket where the only losers are the British public, irrespective of the outcome of the case involved.\r\n \r\nEnter the country illegally and you could have a lawyer at your service funded by the British taxpayers.\r\n \r\nWe call upon the Government to limit Legal Aid to no more than two hours.\r\n \r\nFurther costs should be paid for by the individuals themselves.\r\n",
        "background": "Millions of pounds are spent on legal aid every year. This is taxpayers' money - OUR money!",
